fo%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Miracle+Cure&amp;rft.pub=Vassar+College&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Finnovators.vassar.edu%2Finnovator.html%3Fid%3D77&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGladys+Lounsbury+Hobby\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Oatman, Eric (Winter 2005). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cumc.columbia.edu/psjournal/archive/winter-2005/drug.html\">\"The Drug That Changed the World\"</a>. Volume 25, No. 1. Journal of the College of Physicians and Surgeons: The College of Physicians &amp; Surgeons of Columbia University<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">9 December</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Drug+That+Changed+the+World&amp;rft.place=Journal+of+the+College+of+Physicians+and+Surgeons&amp;rft.series=Volume+25%2C+No.+1&amp;rft.pub=The+College+of+Physicians+%26+Surgeons+of+Columbia+University&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.aulast=Oatman&amp;rft.aufirst=Eric&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cumc.columbia.edu%2Fpsjournal%2Farchive%2Fwinter-2005%2Fdrug.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGladys+Lounsbury+Hobby\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">1964-, Oakes, Elizabeth H., (2002-01-01). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/45835614\"><i>International encyclopedia of women scientists</i></a>. Facts on File. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"Internat